    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.01370.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.01370.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
           
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden&#8212;U S America<ptr target="loc.01370_n1"/></name>
                    <date when="1887-03-06">March 6 '87</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>I am feeling fairly in health&#8212;&#38; every thing goes comfortably these
                days&#8212;I went over to the theatre yesterday afternoon&#8212;had a good ride
                &#38; jaunt &#38; performance&#8212;"Clito"&#8212;Wilson Barret<ptr
                    target="loc.01370_n2"/> sent them for me&#8212;enjoyed the whole 
                affair&#8212;have not had any letter from you now for some time&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
